$ %VSINSTALLDIR%

The installation directory of → Windows/development/Visual-Studio[Visual Studio]

This directory contains sub-directories such as
    • Common7
    • DesignTools
    • DIA SDK (The Microsoft Debug Interface Access Software Development Kit (DIA SDK) provides access to debug information stored in program database (→ Windows/development/Visual-Studio/PDB-files[.pdb]) files generated by Microsoft postcompiler tools.)
    • ImportProjects
    • JavaScript
    • Licenses
    • MSBuild
    • SDK
    • Team Tools
    • VB
    • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC[`VC`] (= `%VCINSTALLDIR%`)
    • VC#
    • Xml

sa:
  The path of this directory is stored in the → Windows/registry[registry] under the key
  → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/Software/Wow6432Node/Microsoft/VisualStudio/SxS/VS7[`HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\VisualStudio\SxS\VS7`].
